    "headline": "Corteva Announces Dates for Second Quarter 2026 Earnings Release and Webcast",
    "summary": "Corteva, Inc. (NYSE: CTVA) today announced it will release its second quarter 2026 earnings on Thursday, July 30, 2026, after the stock market close via press release and its website. The earnings will be presented in a live webcast on Friday, July 31, 2026, at 9:00 a.m. Eastern Time.",
